# Environment Variables Template for QuizWorld
# Copy this file to .env and fill in your actual values

# OpenAI API Key (for quiz generation)
OPENAI_API_KEY=your_openai_api_key_here

# Instructions:
# 1. Get your OpenAI API key from: https://platform.openai.com/api-keys
# 2. Copy this file to .env: cp env.template .env
# 3. Replace "your_openai_api_key_here" with your actual API key
# 4. Deploy to PartyKit with: npx partykit deploy
# 5. Set the environment variable: npx partykit env put OPENAI_API_KEY "your-key-here"

# Note: Firebase is handled client-side, so no server credentials needed! 